OL,8,CStage C
OL,10,GLevitation is a popular trope of
OL,11,Gmagical media, but are we actually
OL,12,Gable to defy gravity and suspend
OL,13,Gthings in the air? The short answer is
OL,14,Gyes. And the longer answer is we have
OL,15,Glots of different ways. Using magnets,
OL,16,Gsound, light, and more we’ve levitated
OL,17,Gobjects from single cells to entire
OL,18,Gpassenger trains. We’ll go over the
OL,19,Gbasic principles underpinning each
OL,20,Gapproach, and consider their benefits
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
